OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772107375
OL,3,CFly-tipping cases jump nearly 10% in a
OL,4,Cyear to new highs, council data shows
OL,6,FCommercial waste-dumping remains at
OL,7,F6%. ITV News has recently reported
OL,8,Findustrial-scale incidents pf this
OL,9,Fkind from Hertfordshire and
OL,10,FOxfordshire.
OL,12,FWhich parts of England are the worst
OL,13,Faffected?
OL,15,FThe data from Defra shows there were
OL,16,F53 fly-tipping incidents per 1,000
OL,17,Fpeople in London during the latest
OL,18,Ftime-period. That's more than double
OL,19,Fthe national average of 21.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
