OL,3,CFly-tipping cases jump nearly 10% in a
OL,4,Cyear to new highs, council data shows
OL,6,FCircular Economy Minister, Mary Creagh
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are empowering local
OL,8,Fauthorities to clamp down on waste
OL,9,Fcowboys and restore pride in our local
OL,10,Fareas.
OL,12,F"I share the public's fury at seeing
OL,13,Four streets, parks and fields used as
OL,14,Fdumping grounds. Fly-tippers should
OL,15,Fknow ` if you use your van to trash
OL,16,Four countryside, don't be surprised
OL,17,Fwhen it ends up on the scrapheap.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
