OL,3,CFly-tipping cases jump nearly 10% in a
OL,4,Cyear to new highs, council data shows
OL,6,F"This government is investing in
OL,7,Fcutting-edge technology and boosting
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency funding to put more
OL,9,Fwaste crime officers on the ground,
OL,10,Fwhile introducing tougher checks and
OL,11,Fpenalties for those who break the law."
OL,13,FIn a statement this morning, Circular
OL,14,FEconomy Minister Mary Creagh MP said
OL,15,Fthe government is investing in
OL,16,F"cutting-edge technology" while
OL,17,Fboosting Environment Agency funding to
OL,18,Fput more waste officers on the ground.
